### COPYRIGHT, LICENCE & ATTRIBUTION STATEMENTS:

Unless otherwise stated this work is licensed under the Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 3.0 Unported License. 
For more information visit: http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/3.0/

However because this repository contains data from various sources which are using different licensing models, any uses of the data should include the appropriate attribution statements.

The aggregate data from the UK and Scottish Government is licensed under by the Open Government Licence. The data is free to use for any purpose and should include an attribution statement (as below).

'Contains Public Sector information licensed under the Open Government Licence v1.0.
For more information visit: http://reference.data.gov.uk/id/open-government-licence'

The spatial data from the Ordance Survey Open Data Project is licensed under the Ordance Survey Open Data Licence which incorporates the Open Government Licence. The data is free to us and should include an attribution statement (as below).

'Contains Ordnance Survey data © Crown copyright and database right 2013.
For more information visit: http://www.ordnancesurvey.co.uk/opendata/licensing.html'

The spatial data from the Scottish Government is one of the exceptions as it is licensed under Ordnance Survey Licence 100024655. The data is free to use for non-commercial use but is more restrictive (see below).

'Contains Ordnance Survey data © Crown copyright and database right 2013.
All rights reserved. Ordnance Survey Licence number 100024655.
For more information visit: http://crtb.sedsh.gov.uk/spatialdatadownload/licenc.asp'
